    "description": "Portrait of Mao Zedong facing left on the right.\r\nChina's emblem (Tian'anmen, the \"Gate of Heavenly Peace\", the gate to the forbidden city, with 5 stars above) in the top left.\r\nDesign with flower below 10 and 拾圆 on the left.\r\nDenomination in arabic numerals (10) in top right corner.",
